ty deals, venture capital funding, and other types of fundraising. It also provides loan syndication and underwriting; M&A advisory, including buy-side and sell-side advisory services; and open offer management services. In addition, the company offers private equity advisory services; structured finance advisory services, including promoter and acquisition financing; and corporate finance advisory services, such as scheme of amalgamations, mergers, spin-off transactions, ESOP transactions, foreign remittance, and equity placements, etc.; and certification, opinion, and valuation services. Further, it offers stock and commodity broking services; and valuation and advisory services for foreign investments. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Mumbai, India. Aryaman Financial Services Limited is a subsidiary of Mahshri Enterprises Pvt. Ltd."}}